# EverFlown Logistics - Complete Source Code

This is the complete freight brokerage platform built with React, Express.js, and PostgreSQL.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Set environment variables
DATABASE_URL=your_postgresql_url
SESSION_SECRET=your_session_secret
REPL_ID=your_repl_id

# Initialize database
npm run db:push

# Start development
npm run dev
```

