## Core Features

- Authentication with Replit Auth
- Dashboard with real-time KPIs
- Lead management and conversion
- Customer database
- Carrier network management
- Order processing workflow
- Dispatch operations
- Invoice management
- Follow-up task system
- Manual shipment tracing

## Database Schema

Complete PostgreSQL schema with:
- Users & Sessions (Auth)
- Leads, Customers, Carriers (Core entities)
- Orders, Dispatches (Operations)
- Quotes, Invoices (Financial)
- Follow-ups (Task management)

All tables have proper relations and constraints for data integrity.

## Technology Stack

**Frontend:** React 18, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Shadcn/UI, TanStack Query
**Backend:** Node.js, Express.js, TypeScript, Drizzle ORM
**Database:** PostgreSQL with Neon serverless
**Auth:** Passport.js with OpenID Connect

This is a production-ready freight brokerage platform ready for deployment.